name: J DILLA "OVER A BILLION SERVED" LIMITED EDITION 24 x 36 PRINT (USA SHIPPING)
description:
In 2006, we were asked to create a commemorative poster celebrating the career of Dilla... We used over 3000 pictures, including everyone who has ever worked with Dilla to create this iconic image remembering him... it was limited to a 1000 pieces and sold out in days... Ma Dukes found a small stack in her basement and we're making them available again, each one signed & numbered by Ma Dukes... Don't sleep... When they're gone, they're gone!

100% proceeds going to Ma Dukes.
$25 including shipping anywhere in the USA.
